1e:T8c5,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"How much revenue do locksmiths lose from missed calls?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"The average locksmith misses 5-8 calls daily, with 89% occurring after hours. With lockouts at £80-£250 and security upgrades at £500-£3,000, missing 3 calls per week costs £1,000-£3,000 monthly. Most locksmiths lose 60-70% of potential revenue to unanswered calls."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can AI handle panic calls from locked-out customers?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. AI remains calm, professional, and reassuring during emergency calls — actually better than tired humans at 2am. It captures location, lock type, urgency, and reassures the customer that a locksmith will call back within minutes. The customer gets immediate response rather than voicemail."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How does AI distinguish between a lockout and a security upgrade?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"The AI identifies lockouts by keywords like 'locked out', 'lost keys', 'snapped key', and 'can't get in'. Security upgrades are identified by 'security survey', 'change locks', 'new house', 'burglary', 'smart lock', and 'CCTV'. Each type gets different priority flagging and capture fields."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What's the ROI of 24/7 call answering for locksmiths?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"At £59/month, one night lockout (£180-£250) pays for 3-4 months. Most locksmiths capture 3-5 additional jobs weekly with AI, including high-value security upgrades. ROI typically exceeds 2,500% annually. Commercial contracts and landlord relationships captured after hours provide recurring revenue."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How can locksmiths get more security upgrade work?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"AI captures security upgrade enquiries with full context: trigger event, property details, current security level, and specific interests (smart locks, CCTV, alarms). Follow up within 15 minutes with a professional callback, offer a free security survey, and arrive with product samples and portfolio photos. One captured security upgrade pays for AI for years."}}]}13:["$","div",null,{"className":"min-h-screen bg-[var(--navy-900)] text-white","children":[["$","$L1d",null,{}],["$","script",null,{"id":"blog-post-article-schema","type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BlogPosting\",\"headline\":\"24/7 Call Answering for Locksmiths: Never Miss a Lockout Again\",\"description\":\"Lockouts are the most urgent trade calls. Learn how UK locksmiths capture emergency calls 24/7 with AI call answering. Never miss a lockout again. 2026.\",\"image\":\"https://whoza.ai/og-image.webp\",\"datePublished\":\"2026-06-05\",\"dateModified\":\"2026-06-05\",\"author\":{\"@type\":\"Person\",\"name\":\"Dru McPherson\",\"jobTitle\":\"Founder, whoza.ai\"},\"publisher\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Whoza.ai\",\"logo\":{\"@type\":\"ImageObject\",\"url\":\"https://whoza.ai/og-image.webp\"}},\"mainEntityOfPage\":{\"@type\":\"WebPage\",\"@id\":\"https://whoza.ai/blog/locksmith-24-7-call-answering\"},\"articleSection\":\"Emergency Services\",\"wordCount\":2062,\"inLanguage\":\"en-GB\",\"speakable\":{\"@type\":\"SpeakableSpecification\",\"cssSelector\":[\"article h1\",\"article h2\",\"article p\"]}}"}}],null,["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$1e"}}],"$L1f","$L20","$L21"]}]
